description: From Sun Rise To Sun Set ....This dramatic corner 10 th floor home is flooded with light all day and has wonderful city views from its private balcony.  Ideal one level living in this beautifully appointed 1472 sq ft open floor plan. There is a large en suite master featuring walk in closet and 4 fixture bath.  The sizable 2nd bedroom or office features double glass doors open to living area or closed gives total bedroom privacy with separate entrance from hallway.  The utilitarian kitchen has Viking appliances, double oven & granite countertop open to living dinging... perfect for entertaining.  There are hardwood floors throughout, large closets, 6' windows in all rooms,washer/dryer in unit and garage parking, all in a concierge building.  Located in the up and coming Seaport Area.  Walk to many new restaurants, South Station  T and easy access to main highways and minutes from the airport. Parking space #59 close to elevator.
